'''陈刚'''（{{bd|1964年}}），男，[[湖北|湖北]][[南漳|南漳]]人，[[美国|美国]]纳米热电材料和流体学者，[[美国国家工程院|美国国家工程院]]院士<ref>[http://news.hustonline.net/html/2010-2-19/69102.shtml HUSTONLINE：校友陈刚当选美国国家工程院院士]{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]教授，Pappalardo微纳工程实验室主任，S3TEC中心主任<ref>[http://meche.mit.edu/people/index.html?id=15 MIT MechE-Gang Chen]</ref>。其带领的团队首次打破被公认为物体间热力传导基本法则的「[[黑体辐射定律|黑体辐射定律]]」公式，证实物体极度近距时的热力传导，可以高到定律所预测的千倍。<ref>[http://news.hustonline.net/html/2009-8-2/64483.shtml HUSTONLINE：校友陈刚破百年物理定律“黑体辐射定律”]{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2009/heat-0729.html MIT：Breaking the law, at the nanoscale]</ref>

2021年1月，美國司法部根據「[[中国行动计划|中國行動計劃]]」拘捕陈刚，指控他在提交聯邦撥款申請時未披露與多個中國教育項目的聯繫。<ref name="fnl">{{cite web|title=MIT Faculty Letter to President Reif in Support of Gang Chen|url=https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/faculty-letter-to-president-reif-in-support-of-professor-gang-chen/|access-date=29 January 2021|author=170 MIT Faculty|date=26 January 2021|website=MIT Faculty Newsletter|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322015027/https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/faculty-letter-to-president-reif-in-support-of-professor-gang-chen/|archive-date=22 March 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>陈刚被捕一事引發美國學術界及科學界的強烈抗議，認為政府是在針對他華裔的身份。<ref name="fnl3">{{cite web|title=MIT Faculty Letter to President Reif in Support of Gang Chen|url=https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/faculty-letter-to-president-reif-in-support-of-professor-gang-chen/|access-date=29 January 2021|author=170 MIT Faculty|date=26 January 2021|website=MIT Faculty Newsletter|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322015027/https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/faculty-letter-to-president-reif-in-support-of-professor-gang-chen/|archive-date=22 March 2021|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Selective prosecution of scientists must stop|journal=Nature Physics|issue=4|doi=10.1038/s41567-021-01231-1|year=2021|volume=17|pages=419–419|issn=1745-2473|doi-access=free}}</ref>一年後，聯邦檢察官撤銷了指控，<ref>{{Cite web|title=美國司法部撤銷對MIT華裔教授陳剛指控|url=https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202201/21/AP61ea6006e4b03103e0c55c8c.html|access-date=2022-04-18|work=香港文匯網|language=zh-Hans-HK}}</ref><ref name="wsj">{{cite news|last=Viswanatha|first=Aruna|date=14 January 2022|title=Prosecutors Recommend Dropping Case Over China Ties Against MIT Scientist|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/prosecutors-recommend-dropping-case-over-china-ties-against-mit-scientist-11642177123|work=Wall Street Journal|location=New York, New York|access-date=14 January 2022|quote=Federal prosecutors have recommended that the Justice Department drop criminal charges against a Massachusetts Institute of Technology mechanical engineering professor accused of hiding his China ties, according to people familiar with the matter...|archive-date=14 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114162549/https://www.wsj.com/articles/prosecutors-recommend-dropping-case-over-china-ties-against-mit-scientist-11642177123|url-status=live}}</ref>指有證據表明聯邦政府實際上並未要求申請人需要做相關披露。<ref name="wp">{{cite news|last1=Nakashima|first1=Ellen|last2=Nakamura|first2=David|date=14 January 2022|title=In high-profile case against MIT’s Gang Chen, prosecutors seeking to drop charges|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/gang-chen-charges-drop-china/2022/01/14/51bae1e2-6f59-11ec-b9fc-b394d592a7a6_story.html|work=The Washington Post|location=Washington DC|access-date=20 January 2022|quote=Prosecutors alleged Chen failed to disclose ties to the Chinese government and a technology university in Shenzhen. But when they interviewed MIT grant administrators in early 2021, after the charges were filed, those officials said the application form Chen filled out in 2017 did not require disclosures such as ties to foreign institutions, according to one person.|archive-date=14 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114200931/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/gang-chen-charges-drop-china/2022/01/14/51bae1e2-6f59-11ec-b9fc-b394d592a7a6_story.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=「我們在殘害我們自己」：華裔教授陳剛案背後的憤怒與幻滅|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20220125/gang-chen-mit-china/zh-hant/|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2022-01-26|last=Barry|first=Ellen|work=紐約時報中文網|language=zh-cmn-hant|quote=上週，政府撤銷了針對陳剛的案件，該案指控他在向美國能源部申請270萬美元撥款的過程中隱瞞了與中國有關的七個關係。檢察官宣布，他們收到了新的信息，表明陳剛沒有義務披露這些關係，使得此案難以成立。}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
1984年获[[华中工学院|华中工学院]]（[[华中科技大学|华中科技大学]]前身）动力系学士学位，1987年获[[华中工学院|华中工学院]]动力系硕士学位。1993年获[[加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校|加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校]]机械系博士学位。<ref>{{cite thesis|last=Chen|first=Gang|date=1993|title=Microscale thermal phenomena in optical and optoelectronic thin-film devices|publisher=University of California, Berkeley|degree=PhD|oclc=892822584|url=https://www.proquest.com/docview/304044659|access-date=18 January 2022|url-status=live|archive-date=19 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119062920/https://www.proquest.com/docview/304044659}}</ref>1993年至1997年任[[杜克大学|杜克大学]]助理教授。1997年至2001年任[[加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校|加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校]]副教授。2001年任职于[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Solar steam generation by heat localization|first1=Hadi|last2=Ni|first2=George|date=21 July 2014|journal=Nature Communications|doi=10.1038/ncomms5449|volume=5|pages=4449|pmid=25043613|last3=Marconnet|first3=Amy Marie|last4=Loomis|first4=James|last5=Yerci|first5=Selcuk|last6=Miljkovic|first6=Nenad|last7=Chen|first7=Gang|last1=Ghasemi|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Bulk nanostructured thermoelectric materials: current research and future prospects|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1039/B822664B|first1=A. J.|last2=Dresselhaus|first2=M. S.|journal=Energy Environ. Sci.|issue=5|doi=10.1039/B822664B|year=2009|volume=2|pages=466–479|last3=Ren|first3=Z. F.|last4=Chen|first4=G.|archive-date=3 May 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503191300/https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2009/EE/b822664b|last1=Minnich|access-date=16 January 2021|author-link2=Mildred Dresselhaus|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Thermal conductivity and ballistic-phonon transport in the cross-plane direction of superlattices|url=https://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevB.57.14958|first1=Gang|journal=Phys. Rev. B|issue=23|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.57.14958|year=1998|volume=57|pages=14958–14973|last1=Chen|access-date=16 January 2021|archive-date=3 May 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503191304/https://journals.aps.org/prb/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevB.57.14958|url-status=live}}</ref>

== 「中國行動計劃」被拘捕 ==
2021年1月14日早上六點半，10到20名FBI特工來到他家中，指控陈刚在提交美國能源部撥款申請時涉嫌未披露與中國相關的聯繫，而將他拘捕。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=「我們在殘害我們自己」：華裔教授陳剛案背後的憤怒與幻滅|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20220125/gang-chen-mit-china/zh-hant/|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2022-01-26|last=Barry|first=Ellen|work=紐約時報中文網|language=zh-cmn-hant}}</ref><ref name="usatty">{{cite web|title=MIT Professor Arrested and Charged with Grant Fraud|url=https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/mit-professor-arrested-and-charged-grant-fraud|access-date=15 January 2021|author=<!--Not stated-->|date=14 January 2021|website=U.S. Attorney's Office, Massachusetts|publisher=Department of Justice, U.S. Attorney’s Office, District of Massachusetts|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115011544/https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/mit-professor-arrested-and-charged-grant-fraud|archive-date=15 January 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>他其後被正式起訴未向美國通報與中國實體的聯繫、電匯欺詐，未在某些納稅年度提交外國銀行賬戶報告、作出虛假陳述。<ref name="special">{{cite web|title=Affidavit of Special Agent Matthew J. McCarthy|url=https://assets.documentcloud.org/documents/20452311/gang-chen-federal-affidavit.pdf|access-date=15 January 2021|author=Matthew J. McCarthy|date=13 January 2021|website=documentcloud.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115101821/https://assets.documentcloud.org/documents/20452311/gang-chen-federal-affidavit.pdf|archive-date=15 January 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>陈刚被捕後[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]校长[[雷欧·拉斐尔·莱夫|雷欧·拉斐尔·莱夫]]发出公開信表示︰「惊讶、非常沮丧且难以理解」。<ref>{{cite news|last=Reif|first=Rafael|date=14 January 2021|title=Distressing news about Professor Gang Chen|url=https://news.mit.edu/2021/professor-gang-chen-fraud-0114|work=MIT News|location=Cambridge, Massachusetts|access-date=15 January 2021}}</ref>2021年1月21日，麻省理工學院100多名教職員工向校長提交聯署信抗議拘捕行動，並指在訴訟書中有「嚴重缺陷和誤導性陳述」，最後以「我們都是陳剛」收結。<ref>[https://new.qq.com/omn/20210123/20210123A04IHN00.html MIT教授联名信：对陈刚的大部分指控是对全体MIT教授的指控]，腾讯新闻。</ref><ref name="fnl4">{{cite web|title=MIT Faculty Letter to President Reif in Support of Gang Chen|url=https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/faculty-letter-to-president-reif-in-support-of-professor-gang-chen/|access-date=29 January 2021|author=170 MIT Faculty|date=26 January 2021|website=MIT Faculty Newsletter|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322015027/https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/faculty-letter-to-president-reif-in-support-of-professor-gang-chen/|archive-date=22 March 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>

FBI文件稱，陳刚從[[南方科技大學|中國南方科技大學]]處獲得了1900萬美元。<ref name="usatty3">{{cite web|title=MIT Professor Arrested and Charged with Grant Fraud|url=https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/mit-professor-arrested-and-charged-grant-fraud|access-date=15 January 2021|author=<!--Not stated-->|date=14 January 2021|website=U.S. Attorney's Office, Massachusetts|publisher=Department of Justice, U.S. Attorney’s Office, District of Massachusetts|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115011544/https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/mit-professor-arrested-and-charged-grant-fraud|archive-date=15 January 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>2021年1月22日，麻省理工學院校長發表第二份聲明，指出那些資金不是給陈刚的，而是麻省理工學院與南方科技大學合作的資金，陈刚只是作為麻省理工的代表負責資金的流向。<ref>{{cite news|last=O'Leary|first=Mary Beth|date=19 June 2018|title=MIT and SUSTech announce Centers for Mechanical Engineering Research and Education at MIT and SUSTech|url=https://news.mit.edu/2018/centers-mechanical-engineering-research-education-mit-sustech-0619|work=MIT News|location=Cambridge, Massachusetts|access-date=15 January 2021|archive-date=15 January 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115172558/https://news.mit.edu/2018/centers-mechanical-engineering-research-education-mit-sustech-0619|url-status=live}}</ref>

司法部的起訴書引起了許多批評， 更多麻省理工學院教師共同簽署了抗議信，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Why Have We, a Group of MIT Faculty, Signed the Letter in Support of Gang Chen?|url=https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/why-have-we-a-group-of-mit-faculty-signed-the-letter-in-support-of-gang-chen/|access-date=2022-01-22|date=2021-02-27|website=MIT Faculty Newsletter|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122232748/https://fnl.mit.edu/january-february-2021/why-have-we-a-group-of-mit-faculty-signed-the-letter-in-support-of-gang-chen/|archive-date=2022-01-22|url-status=live}}</ref>並表示「為陳剛辯護就是為我們珍視的科學辯護」。<ref name="globe">{{cite news|last=Fernandes|first=Deirdre|date=22 January 2021|title=MIT president and faculty members defend professor arrested for China ties|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/01/23/metro/mit-president-faculty-members-defend-professor-arrested-china-ties/|work=Boston Globe|location=Boston, Massachusetts|access-date=23 January 2021|quote=These funds are about advancing the work of a group of colleagues, and the research and educational mission of MIT.|archive-date=24 January 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124092957/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2021/01/23/metro/mit-president-faculty-members-defend-professor-arrested-china-ties/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="nyt26012021">{{cite news|last=Barry|first=Ellen|date=26 January 2021|title=A Scientist Is Arrested, and Academics Push Back|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/26/us/mit-scientist-charges.html|work=The New York Times|location=New York, New York|access-date=29 January 2021|quote=The U.S. is playing into China’s hands by prosecuting researchers it ought to be welcoming.|archive-date=29 January 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129012628/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/26/us/mit-scientist-charges.html|url-status=live}}</ref>麻省理工學院的一位研究人員表示，司法部的「中國行動計劃」從根本意義上就錯誤理解了國際的研究合作。<ref name="wbur">{{cite news|last=Larkin|first=Max|date=29 January 2021|title=MIT Faculty Rally Around Professor Charged With Concealing China Ties|url=https://www.wbur.org/edify/2021/01/29/mit-faculty-letter-gang-chen-china|work=WBUR|location=Boston, Massachusetts|access-date=29 January 2021|quote=Most of the time, the more you read, the more you understand. In this case, the more I read of that complaint, the less I understood.|archive-date=30 January 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130002202/https://www.wbur.org/edify/2021/01/29/mit-faculty-letter-gang-chen-china|url-status=live}}</ref>

2021年9月，檢方向陳刚提出延期起訴協議，這將使他能夠重回工作崗位，未來還能申請政府資助，但作為回報他必須承認與中國有關係，陳刚拒絕。<ref name=":0" />

2022年1月14日，華爾街日報報導稱聯邦檢察官已建議撤銷對陳教授的刑事指控。<ref name="wsj2">{{cite news|last=Viswanatha|first=Aruna|date=14 January 2022|title=Prosecutors Recommend Dropping Case Over China Ties Against MIT Scientist|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/prosecutors-recommend-dropping-case-over-china-ties-against-mit-scientist-11642177123|work=Wall Street Journal|location=New York, New York|access-date=14 January 2022|quote=Federal prosecutors have recommended that the Justice Department drop criminal charges against a Massachusetts Institute of Technology mechanical engineering professor accused of hiding his China ties, according to people familiar with the matter...|archive-date=14 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114162549/https://www.wsj.com/articles/prosecutors-recommend-dropping-case-over-china-ties-against-mit-scientist-11642177123|url-status=live}}</ref>同一天，華盛頓郵報報導說，美國能源部其實並沒有要求陳剛透露他與中國教育項目的聯繫，這令聯邦指控的基礎嚴重削弱。<ref name="wp3">{{cite news|last1=Nakashima|first1=Ellen|last2=Nakamura|first2=David|date=14 January 2022|title=In high-profile case against MIT’s Gang Chen, prosecutors seeking to drop charges|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/gang-chen-charges-drop-china/2022/01/14/51bae1e2-6f59-11ec-b9fc-b394d592a7a6_story.html|work=The Washington Post|location=Washington DC|access-date=20 January 2022|quote=Prosecutors alleged Chen failed to disclose ties to the Chinese government and a technology university in Shenzhen. But when they interviewed MIT grant administrators in early 2021, after the charges were filed, those officials said the application form Chen filled out in 2017 did not require disclosures such as ties to foreign institutions, according to one person.|archive-date=14 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114200931/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/gang-chen-charges-drop-china/2022/01/14/51bae1e2-6f59-11ec-b9fc-b394d592a7a6_story.html|url-status=live}}</ref>2022年1月20日，美国司法部撤销了对其的犯罪指控<ref>{{Cite web|title=Statement from U.S. Attorney Rachael S. Rollins on the Dismissal of the Gang Chen Case|url=https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/statement-us-attorney-rachael-s-rollins-dismissal-gang-chen-case|access-date=2022-03-05|date=2022-01-20|language=en|archive-url=https://archive.ph/7HJiP|archive-date=2022-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在指控撤销後，陳刚接受紐約時報訪問，表示過去一年的經歷「令人痛苦」，指是這個國家的悲哀也讓他理想幻滅，並表示已沒有信心申請美國政府的研究基金。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=捲入「中國計畫」 華裔教授陳剛：對美幻滅|url=https://udn.com/news/story/7332/6062134|access-date=2022-04-18|date=20220126T152014Z|last=聯合新聞網|work=聯合新聞網|language=zh-Hant-TW}}</ref>

